  "body": "[![](https://i.imgur.com/vQ2UgRz.gif)](https://www.instagram.com/pickleakin)[![](https://i.imgur.com/W8FEOyq.gif)](https://www.youtube.com/@PickleAkin)[![](https://i.imgur.com/GvqAUA2.gif)](https://discord.gg/Zz9YP2Cwyq)[![](https://i.imgur.com/rLsNzf1.gif)]([https://i.imgur.com/rLsNzf1.gif](https://www.patreon.com/c/pickleakin?utm_medium=unknown&utm_source=join_link&utm_campaign=creatorshare_creator&utm_content=copyLink&redirect=true))[![](https://i.imgur.com/MPIWGOf.gif)![](https://i.imgur.com/LQ8KYvw.gif)![](https://i.imgur.com/3DFMc0X.gif)](https://bio.link/pickleakin)\n\n**<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">Enjoy the game!<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/tr/thumb/3/32/Minecraft_logo.svg/512px-Minecraft_logo.svg.png?20220324173022\" alt=\"\" width=\"163\" height=\"28\"></span>**\n\n***\n\n### Versions:\n\n#### **![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_1a463678-c383-40a7-9768-e6acbfa4cbc7.png)****<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">H1<a href=\"nick\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hide name</a> <span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">- </span><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 194, 107);\">Works on Client &amp; Server</span></span>**\n\n**![](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1utJPDuqUF3dYA_kH6X1b7Ik9bUQeitq8/view?usp=sharing)![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_a0cf5d24-b729-4cff-8eb2-623e67c37226.png)<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>File Name:</strong></span> Download files named <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">\"H1\"</span>**\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #95a5a6;\">If you are a server owner, just upload it to the server:no need to install it on the client.</span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">/hidename open <span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">- </span></span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"color: #7e8c8d;\">Hides all players'name</span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #95a5a6;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">/hidename close<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"> <span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">- </span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\"><span style=\"color: #7e8c8d;\">Shows all players'name</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><h4><img style=\"font-weight: 400; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_e73816bf-ec55-4089-a874-0608f7aae600.png\" width=\"354\" height=\"118\"></h4></div>\n\n#### **![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_1a463678-c383-40a7-9768-e6acbfa4cbc7.png)****<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">H2<a href=\"nick\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hide Name Behind Blocks</a> <span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">-</span> </span>** <span style=\"color: rgb(45, 194, 107);\"><strong>Works on Client &amp; Server</strong></span>\n\n**__<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_a0cf5d24-b729-4cff-8eb2-623e67c37226.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"35\" height=\"35\">File Name:</strong></span> Download files named <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">\"H2\"</span>__**\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><p><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #95a5a6;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong>If you are a server owner, just upload it to the server:no need to install it on the client.</span></span></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">/hideblockopen <span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">- </span></span></strong></span></strong>Hide player names when behind a block;names appear when in the open</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">/hidename close - </span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color: #95a5a6;\">Shows player names again,even behind blocks.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/apsWVtt.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"299\" height=\"168\"></h4></div>\n\n \n\n#### **![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_1a463678-c383-40a7-9768-e6acbfa4cbc7.png)**<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>H3 <a href=\"nick\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hide selected name</a> </strong></span> **<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">-</span> </span>** <span style=\"color: rgb(45, 194, 107);\"><strong>Works on Client &amp; Server</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_a0cf5d24-b729-4cff-8eb2-623e67c37226.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"35\" height=\"35\">File Name:</strong></span> Download files named <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">\"H3\"</span>\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><p><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #95a5a6;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong>If you are a server owner, just upload it to the server:no need to install it on the client.</span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">/hidename open <span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">- </span></span></strong></span></strong>Hides all players'name</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">/hidename close<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"> <span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">- </span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></strong>Shows all players'name</p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">/hidename</span> <span style=\"color: #3598db;\">\"player name\"<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"> <span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">- </span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color: #7e8c8d;\">Hides only that player's name</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">/hidename default</span> <span style=\"color: #3598db;\">\"player name\"<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"> <span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">- </span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color: #7e8c8d;\">Resets that player's name visibility to default</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #7e8c8d;\"><img style=\"font-weight: 400; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8xqpr2u.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"280\" height=\"179\"></span></p></div>\n\n#### **![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_1a463678-c383-40a7-9768-e6acbfa4cbc7.png)**<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>H4[NICK CHANGE]</strong></span>**<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">-</span> </span>** <span style=\"color: rgb(45, 194, 107);\"><strong>Works on Client &amp; Server</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_a0cf5d24-b729-4cff-8eb2-623e67c37226.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"35\" height=\"35\">File Name:</strong></span> Download files named <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">\"H4\"</span>\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><p><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #95a5a6;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong>If you are a server owner, just upload it to the server:no need to install it on the client.</span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">/nickchange </span><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">\"player name\" \"tag to add\"&nbsp;</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">- </span></span></strong></span></strong>Adds a tag next to the player's name</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">/nickchange default <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">\"old player name\"</span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">- </span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></strong>Resets the selected player's tag</p><p><strong>&nbsp; <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">/nickchange alldefault</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">- </span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color: #7e8c8d;\">Resets all players' tags</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">&nbsp; <strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">/nickmeter <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">\"</span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">on\" </span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><span style=\"color: #95a5a6;\">or</span></span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">&nbsp; <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">\"off\"</span> <span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">- </span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color: #7e8c8d;\">(Player#1,#X Adds player counter like] (The player turns off the counter like)</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #7e8c8d;\"><img style=\"font-weight: 400;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NCWbvYf.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"265\" height=\"346\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RtjEWZ3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"428\" height=\"265\"></span></span></p></div>\n\n#### **![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_1a463678-c383-40a7-9768-e6acbfa4cbc7.png)**<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>H5</strong></span>[**<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">Hide name</span>**](nick) **- undefined** <span style=\"color: rgb(45, 194, 107);\"><strong>Works on Client&nbsp;</strong></span>  \n\n<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_a0cf5d24-b729-4cff-8eb2-623e67c37226.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"35\" height=\"35\">File Name:</strong></span> Download files named <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">\"H5\"</span>\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong>It's enough to install it on the client; it works on all servers. There's no need to install it on the server as well.</p><p><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color: #95a5a6;\">Press the<strong> \"<span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">F12\"</span></strong> <span style=\"color: #b96ad9;\"><strong>key</strong></span> to hide player names, press it again to show them.</span></span><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/w2AZz1N.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"426\" height=\"240\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n\n \n\n#### **![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_1a463678-c383-40a7-9768-e6acbfa4cbc7.png)**<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>H6[</strong></span><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>Show Players' Health</strong></span><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>(nick) -<span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\"> </span></strong></span> <span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\">Works on Client</span>&nbsp;</strong></span>  \n\n**<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_a0cf5d24-b729-4cff-8eb2-623e67c37226.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"35\" height=\"35\">File Name:</span> Download files named <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">\"H6\"</span>**\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong>It's enough to install it on the client; it works on all servers. There's no need to install it on the server as well.</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>There are key changes in som</strong></span><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">e versions</strong></p><p><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_0626bbd1-0d64-479c-ba37-30c05f33629e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #7e8c8d;\">Press <strong><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">\"F6,F7,F9\" <span style=\"color: #b96ad9;\">key</span></span></strong> to show player health within a 5-block radius/ Press<strong> <span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #7e8c8d;\"><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">\"F6,F7,F9\"</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #b96ad9;\">key</span></strong> again to hide it</span></span></span></span></span></p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Cq32XIj.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"424\" height=\"239\"></div>\n\n#### **![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_1a463678-c383-40a7-9768-e6acbfa4cbc7.png)**<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>T1[</strong></span><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>Show Item Names on the Ground] </strong></span> **<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\">-</span> </span>** <span style=\"color: rgb(45, 194, 107);\"><strong>Works on Client &amp; Server</strong></span>\n\n**<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1200277/description_a0cf5d24-b729-4cff-8eb2-623e67c37226.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"35\" height=\"35\">File Name:</span> Download files named <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">\"T1\"</span>**\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q7jwndL.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\"></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: 